A MajorMode for editing GNAT project files is available in GNU ELPA (the Emacs Lisp Package Archive).

Project page:

* https://elpa.gnu.org/packages/doc/gpr-mode.html

The current [::gpr-mode] maintainer is StephenLeake, [http://stephe-leake.org/] who maintains the code in GNU ELPA and periodically publishes updated versions on the project page.

Related packages:

[::ada-mode] - a major mode for editing Ada files.

[::gpr-query] - uses the cross reference information output by the gnat compiler to provide an Emacs xref backend. 

